\left.\frac{\partial^{2}f}{\partial x^{2}}\right|_{x=0}=0\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula \[
\frac{\partial^{3}f}{\partial x^{3}}=-24\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $\therefore$
\end_inset

 there is a pitchfork bifurcation at 
\begin_inset Formula $\left(0,0\right)$
\end_inset

.
